text.tspan: RCON/OP "/ugetblock x y z world" command to query block data remotely for external scripting.
Read container contents from blockstate of any block:
Return this data to webserver script and proceed accordingly.
Optionally specify world as last parameter. Default is: "minecraft:overworld"

Any user may 'use', but only obtained via /give command.
RCON/OP "/usetblock x y z world blockdata [keep/destroy/replace]" to set a block silently.
